label: The Sunday Telegraph
title: The_Sunday_Telegraph_(Sydney)
exrest: The Sunday Telegraph is an Australian tabloid newspaper, the separately published Sunday edition of The Daily Telegraph. It is available throughout Sydney, across most of regional and remote New South Wales, the Australian Capital Territory and South East Queensland. As of 2012, The Sunday Telegraph is Australia's biggest selling newspaper.
